window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Lennon Montgomery is scared sh-tless of love. </p> <p>When the floor fell out from underneath her perfect childhood, it shattered her ability to trust. The one man in her life who was genetically programmed to love her left her. Since then she's allowed men into her bed and even into her life but never into her heart. </p> <p>Until him. </p> <p>Jamison Henley is content living his life and loving only three things: making guitars, cooking great food, and Martha, his pit bull. He never chases women, and he's never had to. </p> <p>Until her. </p> <p>One night together changes everything. There's no going back to the way it was before. She doesn't want to want him, but she does. He knows he wants her, but he can't have her. </p> <p>Will Montgomery take the leap of faith in choosing Henley? Or will her fear cripple their chance at a happily ever after? </p>"; 
